Directives:
1.Directives HTML ko daynamic kr deta hai
2.Directives DOM kai structure and bheviour ko change krta hai.
3.Hum Directly HTML pr ngFor loop if else condition lga skte hai by Directives.


__________Angular mai Directives ko three bhago mai bata gya hai____________
1.Component Directives
2.Stractual Directives
3.Attribute Directives

*Component Directives: Jb component khi load hota hai to tbhi component "Component Directive" khelata hai

*Stractual Directives: Jiske sath Star lga hota hai Stratual Directive khe lata hai, like *ngIF,*ngFor,@ngSwitch,

*Attribute Directives:Attribute Directive DOM kai bheviour ko chnage krta hai.